'''Pierre Dauzier''' (31 January 1939 in Périgueux – 28 September 2007 in Paris) was a [[France|French]] businessman.<ref>{{cite web|title=lesescho.fr|url=http://www.lesechos.fr/01/10/2007/lesechos.fr/300206496_deces-de-pierre-dauzier.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=whoswho.fr|url=http://www.whoswho.fr/decede/biographie-pierre-dauzier_8008}}</ref>

